  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Disclosure by Law and Protection of Farlex If we are required by law to disclose certain information to local state federal national or international law enforcement authorities we will do so We will also disclose information to third parties as necessary in order to comply with applicable laws and regulations In addition Farlex may share information in order to investigate prevent or take action regarding illegal activities or suspected fraud or enforce or apply our agreements</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

